  [Text] Cairo, 25 Jan (MENA) -- An official in the Supreme 
State Security Prosecution has stated that the security agencies 
succeeded in capturing a number of automatic rifles and 
explosives in an arms cache in the Hulwan district on 
information provided by terrorist Muhammad Ahmad Farhan, who was 
arrested during the al-Ma'sarah incidents last week. 
