<H3> <TI>   Israel's Weizman Announces Cooperation in Antiterror Fight </TI></H3>
<H4>   Wants to Pursue Joint Investments </H4>
<F P=102> TA2701115494 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1100 
GMT 27 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2701115494 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>


