<H4>   URNG Reportedly Downs Power Tower, Causes Blackout </H4>
<F P=102> PA2801152994 Guatemala City Cadena de Emisoras Unidas in 
Spanish 1400 GMT 28 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2801152994 </F>
