<H3> <TI>   Islamic Jihad Calls for `Toppling' Palestinian Negotiators </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  JN0302192794 (Clandestine) Al-Quds Palestinian Arab Radio in 
Arabic 1730 GMT 3 Feb 94 </F>

