<H3> <TI>   Security Agencies Investigate Amman Theater Explosion </TI></H3>
<H4>   Bomb in Projector Room </H4>
<F P=102> JN2601142594 Amman Radio Jordan Network in Arabic 1406 GMT 
26 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN2601142594 </F>
<F P=104>  Amman Radio Jordan Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A responsible source at the Ministry of Interior has 
stated that at 1255 today, Wednesday, 26 January 1994, an 
explosion took place at Cinema Revoli, located in Saqf al-Sayl, 
Quraysh Street, when a film was being shown. 
  The explosion took place in the projector room, which is 
situated in the theater's second floor. The explosion wounded 
seven people, one seriously. There was also some material 
damage to the theater. The wounded were admitted to a hospital. 
The competent security agencies are investigating the incident 
to determine its causes. 

</TEXT>

