<H3> <TI>   Security Agencies Investigate Amman Theater Explosion </TI></H3>
<H4>   Interior Minister Names Two Arrestees </H4>
<F P=102> JN0602134094 Amman Radio Jordan Network in Arabic 1200 GMT 6 
Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0602134094 </F>
<F P=104>  Amman Radio Jordan Network </F>


